title: ComicPirates Weeklies Index (CPWI) (2012-04 - 2014-10) (N=102k)
description:
CONTAINS:       Consistently formatted and variously sorted plaintext indeces for
the weekly (or monthly or annual) comics releases posted in the stated period by <a href="
http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipJ" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipJ</a>   and  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipjolly" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/user/shipjolly</a>   .

DETAILS:        First = 2012-04-11   |   Last = 2014-10-29   |   Count = 102,551

FORMATTING:     The original data stems directly from the contents of the metadata files (see  <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10989336" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/10989336</a>   ), and was automatically processed to put each entry into the following standardized format:

   |t>14-09-10 0000|s>  912,274,022|n>Spacehawk (2012) (Digital) (Bean-Empire).cbz

   |t>   Timestamp; two digits each for year, month, day, hour, minute of release.
   The time-of-day part is always 0000 and functions only as a placeholder here.

   |s>   Filesize in bytes, formatted for improved legibility. Fixed-width field
   with a 10-gigabyte maximum; fingers crossed that'll suffice for a while yet!

   |n>   Filename, including extension.

ORGANIZATION:   Each of the contained files is sorted by a combination of two of those three fields, as no single one is ever entirely unique by itself, due to duplicate contents and identical naming and so on: By name then time (filename suffix "by nt"), by size then name ("by sn"), and by time then name ("by tn").

LIVE VERSION:  <a href=" http://gesserit.000space.com/www/cpwi" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://gesserit.000space.com/www/cpwi</a>
